  Welcome to Week 2

Welcome to Week #2

While last week we discussed the basics of working with AI for storytelling, this week is all about getting into the nitty gritty of how to actually direct your overall art styles.

The goal of this week is for you to be able to create video animatics that accurately portray your desired film style.

This Week You'll Learn:

  • Advanced Midjourney Settings
  • Directing Composition and Set Design Midjourney
  • Technical Cinematography Decisions for Stylizing
  • Voice Overs
  • Creating New Voices
  • Cloning Voices
  • Basic Face Animation in D-ID (Advanced Will Be in Week #4)
  • How to Edit Video in Premiere Pro
  • Pulling Music
  • Title Design Basics

By the end of week #2, you'll be able to create a video-based pitch and concept trailer. By learning these skills you will be able to visually show your film style in a way that we only dreamed was possible just a few months ago.
